Snyak.


-----Original Message-----
From: mark mark [mailto:markerob@...]
Sent: Wednesday, June 09, 1999 2:14 PM
To: warriors_eq@onelist.com
Subject: Re: [warriors_eq] [warrior_eq] Charisma
necklaces spoiler

From: mark mark <markerob@...>

I don't know if everyone knows about this but I'll post it
just in case.

Drosco in the Qeynos aquiducts has a +5 to char medal on
him,and he is an
easy kill. Prob lev 8 or so. It is a lore item though, so
you will not be
able to get more than one. It is better to enter the sewers
in the pool near
the qeynos bank, that is closer to his spawn.

There is also a nesting rat down there that has a gold
necklace +3 to
charisma. I don't know what quest it is related to, but it
is not a lore
item so you could prob get more than one (not sure), anyway
the rat is a
very easy kill. Prob lev 4-6. If anyone knows what quest
this is for send
me a post, curious.....

Just for everyones information.....

Arathorne, Warrior of Clan Dolald
Solsek Ro
